<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Automation Portfolio — n8n Workflows</title>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  :root {
    --bg: #0f0f0f;
    --bg2: #181818;
    --bg3: #222;
    --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    --border2: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
    --text: #f0f0f0;
    --muted: #888;
    --hint: #555;
    --green: #1D9E75;
    --green-bg: #0d2e22;
    --purple-bg: #1e1a2e;
    --purple: #a89cf7;
    --blue-bg: #0d1e2e;
    --blue: #7ab8f5;
    --pink-bg: #2a1520;
    --pink: #f5a0c0;
    --amber-bg: #2a1f0d;
    --amber: #f0b060;
    --teal-bg: #0d2420;
    --teal: #5dcaa5;
    --radius: 12px;
    --radius-sm: 8px;
  }
  body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* NAV */
  nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border); position: sticky; top: 0; background: rgba(15,15,15,0.92); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); z-index: 10; }
  .nav-logo { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .nav-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--green); }
  .nav-cta { background: var(--text); color: var(--bg); border: none; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); padding: 8px 18px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; }

  /* HERO */
  .hero { padding: 5rem 2rem 4rem; text-align: center; max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; background: var(--bg2); border: 0.5px solid var(--border2); border-radius: 20px; padding: 5px 16px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .badge-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--green); }
  h1 { font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 42px); font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  h1 span { color: var(--green); }
  .hero p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 460px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn { display: inline-block; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); padding: 11px 24px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; transition: opacity .15s; }
  .btn:hover { opacity: .85; }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--text); color: var(--bg); border: none; }
  .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--text); border: 0.5px solid var(--border2); }

  /* STATS */
  .stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 12px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 4rem; padding: 0 2rem; }
  .stat { background: var(--bg2); border: 0.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.25rem; text-align: center; }
  .stat-n { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 500; }
  .stat-l { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 4px; }

  /* PROJECTS */
  .section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem 4rem; }
  .section-header { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; }
  .section-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--hint); letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .filters { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .filter { background: transparent; border: 0.5px solid var(--border2); border-radius: 20px; padding: 5px 14px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); cursor: pointer; transition: all .15s; }
  .filter.active { background: var(--text); color: var(--bg); border-color: transparent; }

  .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 14px; }
  .card { background: var(--bg2); border: 0.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.25rem; transition: border-color .15s, transform .15s; }
  .card:hover { border-color: var(--border2); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .card-top { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .icon { width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .tag { font-size: 11px; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 500; }
  .card h3 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .card p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .card-footer { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding-top: .75rem; border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border); }
  .saved { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--green); }
  .arrow-icon { color: var(--hint); }

  /* PROCESS */
  .process-section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem 4rem; }
  .steps { display: flex; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 4px; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  .step-item { background: var(--bg2); border: 0.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); padding: 8px 16px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); }
  .step-arrow { font-size: 14px; color: var(--hint); }
  .process-note { font-size: 13px; color: var(--hint); margin-top: 1rem; }

  /* TESTIMONIAL */
  .testimonial-section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem 4rem; }
  .tcard { background: var(--bg2); border: 0.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.5rem; }
  .tquote { font-size: 15px; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.7; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .tauthor { font-size: 12px; color: var(--hint); font-weight: 500; }

  /* FOOTER CTA */
  .footer-cta { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto 4rem; padding: 0 2rem; }
  .cta-box { background: var(--bg2); border: 0.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 3rem 2rem; text-align: center; }
  .cta-box h2 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: .5rem; }
  .cta-box p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

  /* DIVIDER */
  .divider { border: none; border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border); margin: 0 2rem 4rem; max-width: 860px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    .stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    nav { padding: .75rem 1rem; }
    .hero { padding: 3rem 1rem 2rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">
    <div class="nav-dot"></div>
    Automation Portfolio
  </div>
  <a href="mailto:your@email.com" class="nav-cta">Book a call</a>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="badge"><span class="badge-dot"></span> Available for new projects</div>
  <h1>I automate the work<br><span>you hate doing</span></h1>
  <p>Custom n8n workflows that save your team hours every week — without changing your existing tools.</p>
  <div class="hero-btns">
    <a href="mailto:your@email.com" class="btn btn-primary">Book a free call →</a>
    <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-ghost">See projects</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="stats">
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-n">8+</div><div class="stat-l">Workflows built</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-n">~40h</div><div class="stat-l">Saved / month</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-n">5</div><div class="stat-l">Domains covered</div></div>
</div>

<div class="section" id="projects">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-label">Projects</div>
    <div class="filters">
      <button class="filter active" onclick="filter('all',this)">All</button>
      <button class="filter" onclick="filter('ai',this)">AI Agents</button>
      <button class="filter" onclick="filter('crm',this)">CRM</button>
      <button class="filter" onclick="filter('social',this)">Social</button>
      <button class="filter" onclick="filter('data',this)">Data</button>
      <button class="filter" onclick="filter('notif',this)">Alerts</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="grid" id="grid">

    <div class="card" data-cat="ai">
      <div class="card-top">
        <div class="icon" style="background:var(--purple-bg)">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="var(--purple)" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="7"/><path d="M7 10h6M10 7v6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="tag" style="background:var(--purple-bg);color:var(--purple)">AI Agent</span>
      </div>
      <h3>Customer support AI agent</h3>
      <p>Reads incoming emails → classifies intent → drafts reply with GPT-4 → sends if confidence is high.</p>
      <div class="card-footer">
        <span class="saved">Saves 15h / week</span>
        <svg class="arrow-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card" data-cat="crm">
      <div class="card-top">
        <div class="icon" style="background:var(--blue-bg)">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="var(--blue)" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="3" y="5" width="14" height="10" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="tag" style="background:var(--blue-bg);color:var(--blue)">CRM</span>
      </div>
      <h3>Lead auto-enrichment</h3>
      <p>New HubSpot lead → finds LinkedIn + company data → enriches the record + assigns to the right sales rep.</p>
      <div class="card-footer">
        <span class="saved">Saves 8h / week</span>
        <svg class="arrow-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card" data-cat="social">
      <div class="card-top">
        <div class="icon" style="background:var(--pink-bg)">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="var(--pink)" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="3"/><path d="M10 3v2M10 15v2M3 10h2M15 10h2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="tag" style="background:var(--pink-bg);color:var(--pink)">Social</span>
      </div>
      <h3>Content calendar autopilot</h3>
      <p>Reads Notion content plan → generates captions with AI → schedules posts on LinkedIn, Twitter & Instagram.</p>
      <div class="card-footer">
        <span class="saved">Saves 6h / week</span>
        <svg class="arrow-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card" data-cat="data">
      <div class="card-top">
        <div class="icon" style="background:var(--amber-bg)">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="var(--amber)" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="3" y="3" width="14" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M7 7h6M7 10h6M7 13h4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="tag" style="background:var(--amber-bg);color:var(--amber)">Data</span>
      </div>
      <h3>Competitor price tracker</h3>
      <p>Scrapes competitor websites daily → compares to your prices → sends alert if gap exceeds threshold.</p>
      <div class="card-footer">
        <span class="saved">Saves 5h / week</span>
        <svg class="arrow-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card" data-cat="notif">
      <div class="card-top">
        <div class="icon" style="background:var(--teal-bg)">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="var(--teal)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M10 2a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v3l1.5 2.5h-15L4 11V8a6 6 0 0 1 6-6zM8.5 17.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 3 0"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="tag" style="background:var(--teal-bg);color:var(--teal)">Alerts</span>
      </div>
      <h3>Smart Slack alerting system</h3>
      <p>Monitors KPIs from Google Sheets → fires Slack alert with context when any metric drops below target.</p>
      <div class="card-footer">
        <span class="saved">Zero missed alerts</span>
        <svg class="arrow-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card" data-cat="ai crm">
      <div class="card-top">
        <div class="icon" style="background:var(--purple-bg)">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="var(--purple)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M4 4h12v8H4zM8 12v4M12 12v4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="tag" style="background:var(--purple-bg);color:var(--purple)">AI + CRM</span>
      </div>
      <h3>Meeting notes → CRM action</h3>
      <p>Transcribes Zoom meeting → extracts action items with AI → creates tasks in CRM + notifies team on Slack.</p>
      <div class="card-footer">
        <span class="saved">Saves 4h / week</span>
        <svg class="arrow-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<hr class="divider">

<div class="process-section">
  <div class="section-label">How it works</div>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step-item">Discovery call</div>
    <span class="step-arrow">→</span>
    <div class="step-item">Workflow design</div>
    <span class="step-arrow">→</span>
    <div class="step-item">Build & test</div>
    <span class="step-arrow">→</span>
    <div class="step-item">Handover + docs</div>
    <span class="step-arrow">→</span>
    <div class="step-item">Ongoing support</div>
  </div>
  <p class="process-note">Typical delivery: 3–7 days per workflow. All workflows include documentation and a walkthrough video.</p>
</div>

<hr class="divider">

<div class="testimonial-section">
  <div class="section-label">What clients say</div>
  <div class="tcard" style="margin-top:1.5rem">
    <div class="tquote">"We were copy-pasting data between 4 tools every morning. Now it's fully automatic and our team actually trusts the data."</div>
    <div class="tauthor">— Operations Manager, SaaS startup</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="footer-cta">
  <div class="cta-box">
    <h2>Got a repetitive process?</h2>
    <p>Tell me what it is — I'll tell you if I can automate it.</p>
    <a href="mailto:your@email.com" class="btn btn-primary">Let's talk →</a>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
function filter(cat, btn) {
  document.querySelectorAll('.filter').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
  btn.classList.add('active');
  document.querySelectorAll('.card').forEach(c => {
    c.style.display = (cat === 'all' || c.dataset.cat.includes(cat)) ? '' : 'none';
  });
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
